  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 180&deg;C/ 160&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Rip the <strong>ciabatta</strong> into small pieces&nbsp;onto one side of a baking tray,&nbsp;drizzle with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a big pinch of <strong>salt</strong> - these are your <strong>croutons</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trim the <strong>green beans</strong> and cut them in half</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Lay out a piece of <strong>foil</strong> and put the <strong>green beans</strong> in the middle</p>\r\n<p>Scrunch up the edges of the foil slightly, then add 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and close the parcel tightly</p>\r\n<p>Add the parcel to the other half of the tray and put it in the oven for 15 min, or until the ciabatta has crisped and the green beans are tender with a slight bite&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>eggs</strong> to a pot of <strong>salted</strong>, boiled water over a high heat (salt prevents the eggs from cracking)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Boil&nbsp;the eggs for exactly 7 min (perfect, mid-boiled eggs)</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, fill a bowl of very cold water with ice (Gousto's ice packs are perfect) ready for step 5 &nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Grate the <strong>cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>mayonnaise</strong>, <strong>vinegar</strong> and <strong>Henderson's relish</strong>, with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Grate in&nbsp;the <strong>garlic</strong> and add half of the <strong>cheese</strong> and half of the <strong>chives</strong> - this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/748.step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
